title: Drawings of Rembrandt vol II (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
Drawings of Rembrandt vol II
Dover Publications | 1965 | ISBN: 0486214869 | English | 306 pages | PDF | 40.6 MB

The stature of Rembrandt as one of the greatest artists of all time is universally accepted. His paintings and etchings display the technical mastery, vitality, and power that all artists strive for and few achieve. Although his drawings seldom attract the same popular attention as his paintings and etchings, they reveal equal greatness
